    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a pinnacle of the 996.2 generation. This example features the 3.6L flat-six power plant with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The wide-body chassis remains structurally perfect, supported by a factory-spec AWD system and the iconic 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc braking system. Mechanically, the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the cooling system has been overhauled with high-flow radiators. Every bushing and linkage in the suspension geometry remains taut, offering the quintessential analog feedback expected of a low-mileage C4S. A turn-key specimen with a flawless service history and original paint depth.",
